    if (sheets[i].ownerNode.dataset["origin"] !== "pandoc") continue;
    try { var rules = sheets[i].cssRules; } catch (e) { continue; }
    for (var j = 0; j < rules.length; j++) {
      var rule = rules[j];
      // check if there is a div.sourceCode rule
      if (rule.type !== rule.STYLE_RULE || rule.selectorText !== "div.sourceCode") continue;
      var style = rule.style.cssText;
      // check if color or background-color is set
      if (rule.style.color === '' && rule.style.backgroundColor === '') continue;
      // replace div.sourceCode by a pre.sourceCode rule
      sheets[i].deleteRule(j);
      sheets[i].insertRule('pre.sourceCode{' + style + '}', j);
    }
  }
})();
</script>

<body>


<div class="container-fluid main-container">




<div id="header">

</div>


<p>Regresi bisa digunakan untuk merepresentasikan hubungan antara dua peubah yaitu peubah respon dan prediktor. Banyak data yang tidak bisa direpresentaskan hanya dengan regresi linear. Oleh karena itu, dikembangkanlah regresi agar bisa merepresentasikan hubungan tak linear tersebut.</p>
<div id="package" class="section level2">
<h2>Package</h2>
<p>Silahkan install jika belum ada</p>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb1"><pre class="sourceCode r"><code class="sourceCode r"><span id="cb1-1"><a href="#cb1-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">install.packages</span>(<span class="st">&quot;tidyverse&quot;</span>)</span>
<span id="cb1-2"><a href="#cb1-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">install.packages</span>(<span class="st">&quot;MultiKink&quot;</span>)</span>
<span id="cb1-3"><a href="#cb1-3" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">install.packages</span>(<span class="st">&quot;rsample&quot;</span>)</span>
<span id="cb1-4"><a href="#cb1-4" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">install.packages</span>(<span class="st">&quot;mlr3measures&quot;</span>)</span>
<span id="cb1-5"><a href="#cb1-5" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">install.packages</span>(<span class="st">&quot;broom&quot;</span>)</span></code></pre></div>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb2"><pre class="sourceCode r"><code class="sourceCode r"><span id="cb2-1"><a href="#cb2-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">library</span>(tidyverse)</span>
<span id="cb2-2"><a href="#cb2-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">library</span>(rsample)</span></code></pre></div>
</div>
<div id="data" class="section level2">
<h2>Data</h2>
<p>Data yang digunakan untuk ilustrasi berasal dari studi antropometri terhadap 892 perempuan di bawah 50 tahun di tiga desa Gambia di Afrika Barat. Data terdiri dari 3 Kolom yaitu Age, Intriceps dan tricepts. Berikut adalah penjelasannya pada masing-masing kolom:</p>
<ul>
<li>age : umur responden</li>
<li>Intriceps : logaritma dari ketebalan lipatan kulit triceps</li>
<li>triceps: ketebalan lipatan kulit triceps</li>
</ul>
<div class="figure">
<img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt />
<p class="caption">Ilustrasi ketebalan lipatan kulit</p>
</div>
<p>Lipatan kulit trisep diperlukan untuk menghitung lingkar otot lengan atas. Ketebalannya memberikan informasi tentang cadangan lemak tubuh, sedangkan massa otot yang dihitung memberikan informasi tentang cadangan protein</p>
<div id="import-data" class="section level3">
<h3>import data</h3>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb3"><pre class="sourceCode r"><code class="sourceCode r"><span id="cb3-1"><a href="#cb3-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">data</span>(<span class="st">&quot;triceps&quot;</span>,<span class="at">package=</span><span class="st">&quot;MultiKink&quot;</span>)</span></code></pre></div>
<p>Jika kita gambarkan dalam bentuk scatterplot</p>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb4"><pre class="sourceCode r"><code class="sourceCode r"><span id="cb4-1"><a href="#cb4-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">ggplot</span>(triceps,<span class="fu">aes</span>(<span class="at">x=</span>age, <span class="at">y=</span>triceps)) <span class="sc">+</span></span>
<span id="cb4-2"><a href="#cb4-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                 <span class="fu">geom_point</span>(<span class="at">alpha=</span><span class="fl">0.55</span>, <span class="at">color=</span><span class="st">&quot;black&quot;</span>) <span class="sc">+</span> </span>
<span id="cb4-3"><a href="#cb4-3" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                 <span class="fu">theme_bw</span>() </span></code></pre></div>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="672" /></p>
<p>Berdasarkan pola hubungan yang terlihat pada scatterplot, kita akan mencoba untuk mencari model yang bisa merepresentasikan pola hubungan tersebut dengan baik.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="smoothing-splines" class="section level2">
<h2>Smoothing Splines</h2>
<p>Menurut Harezlak dan Teixeira-Pinto (2020), pendekatan spline dapat pula dilakukan dengan ide yang mirip seperti yang dilakukan pada regularisasi. Metode <em>smoothing spline</em> menggunakan penalti pada jumlah kuadrat sisaan seperti yang terlihat pada rumus berikut ini: <span class="math display">\[\sum_{i=1}^n {(y_i-f(x_i))}^2+\lambda\int f&#39;&#39;(t)^2 dt\]</span></p>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb5"><pre class="sourceCode r"><code class="sourceCode r"><span id="cb5-1"><a href="#cb5-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>model_sms <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="fu">with</span>(<span class="at">data =</span> triceps,<span class="fu">smooth.spline</span>(age,triceps))</span>
<span id="cb5-2"><a href="#cb5-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>model_sms                  </span></code></pre></div>
<pre><code>## Call:
## smooth.spline(x = age, y = triceps)
## 
## Smoothing Parameter  spar= 0.5162704  lambda= 1.232259e-06 (13 iterations)
## Equivalent Degrees of Freedom (Df): 50.00639
## Penalized Criterion (RSS): 8591.581
## GCV: 13.77835</code></pre>
<p>Fungsi <code>smooth.spline()</code> dapat digunakan untuk melakukan smoothing spline pada R. Sebagai ilustrasi, data <code>triceps</code> yang tersedia di package <code>MultiKink</code> akan digunakan. Pada fungsi <code>smooth.spline()</code> selain parameter <code>lambda</code>, terdapat pula parameter <code>spar</code>yang bisa digunakan untuk mengatur tingkat <code>smoothness</code> dari kurva. Hubungan antara parameter <code>spar</code> dan <code>lambda</code> bisa ditulis dengan persamaan:</p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
 = r\times256^{(3s - 1)}
\]</span> dimana <span class="math inline">\(r = tr(X&#39; W X) / tr()\)</span> <span class="math inline">\(s\)</span> merupakan spar</p>
<p>Kemudian, fungsi <code>smooth.spline</code> secara otomatis memilih paramter <code>lambda</code> terbaik dengan menggunakan Cross-Validation (CV) dan Generalized Cross-Validation (GCV). Perbedaan utama antara keduanya adalah pada ukuran kebaikan model yang digunakan. Kalau CV menggunakan MSE sebagai ukuran kebaikan model, sedangkan GCV menggunakan Weighted-MSE. Banyaknya folds (lipatan) pada CV dan GCV ini adalah sejumlah obserbasinya.</p>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb7"><pre class="sourceCode r"><code class="sourceCode r"><span id="cb7-1"><a href="#cb7-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>pred_data <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> broom<span class="sc">::</span><span class="fu">augment</span>(model_sms)</span>
<span id="cb7-2"><a href="#cb7-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb7-3"><a href="#cb7-3" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">ggplot</span>(pred_data,<span class="fu">aes</span>(<span class="at">x=</span>x,<span class="at">y=</span>y))<span class="sc">+</span></span>
<span id="cb7-4"><a href="#cb7-4" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">geom_point</span>(<span class="at">alpha=</span><span class="fl">0.55</span>, <span class="at">color=</span><span class="st">&quot;black&quot;</span>)<span class="sc">+</span></span>
<span id="cb7-5"><a href="#cb7-5" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">geom_line</span>(<span class="fu">aes</span>(<span class="at">y=</span>.fitted),<span class="at">col=</span><span class="st">&quot;blue&quot;</span>,</span>
<span id="cb7-6"><a href="#cb7-6" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>            <span class="at">lty=</span><span class="dv">1</span>)<span class="sc">+</span></span>
<span id="cb7-7"><a href="#cb7-7" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">xlab</span>(<span class="st">&quot;age&quot;</span>)<span class="sc">+</span></span>
<span id="cb7-8"><a href="#cb7-8" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">ylab</span>(<span class="st">&quot;triceps&quot;</span>)<span class="sc">+</span></span>
<span id="cb7-9"><a href="#cb7-9" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">theme_bw</span>()</span></code></pre></div>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="672" /></p>
<p>Pengaruh parameter <code>lambda</code> terhadap tingkat smoothness kurva bisa dilihat dari ilustrasi berikut:</p>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb8"><pre class="sourceCode r"><code class="sourceCode r"><span id="cb8-1"><a href="#cb8-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>model_sms_lambda <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="fu">data.frame</span>(<span class="at">lambda=</span><span class="fu">seq</span>(<span class="dv">0</span>,<span class="dv">5</span>,<span class="at">by=</span><span class="fl">0.5</span>)) <span class="sc">%&gt;%</span> </span>
<span id="cb8-2"><a href="#cb8-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">group_by</span>(lambda) <span class="sc">%&gt;%</span> </span>
<span id="cb8-3"><a href="#cb8-3" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">do</span>(broom<span class="sc">::</span><span class="fu">augment</span>(<span class="fu">with</span>(<span class="at">data =</span> triceps,<span class="fu">smooth.spline</span>(age,triceps,<span class="at">lambda =</span> .<span class="sc">$</span>lambda))))</span></code></pre></div>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb9"><pre class="sourceCode r"><code class="sourceCode r"><span id="cb9-1"><a href="#cb9-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>p <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="fu">ggplot</span>(model_sms_lambda,</span>
<span id="cb9-2"><a href="#cb9-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>       <span class="fu">aes</span>(<span class="at">x=</span>x,<span class="at">y=</span>y))<span class="sc">+</span></span>
<span id="cb9-3"><a href="#cb9-3" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">geom_line</span>(<span class="fu">aes</span>(<span class="at">y=</span>.fitted),</span>
<span id="cb9-4"><a href="#cb9-4" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>            <span class="at">col=</span><span class="st">&quot;blue&quot;</span>,</span>
<span id="cb9-5"><a href="#cb9-5" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>            <span class="at">lty=</span><span class="dv">1</span></span>
<span id="cb9-6"><a href="#cb9-6" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>            )<span class="sc">+</span></span>
<span id="cb9-7"><a href="#cb9-7" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">facet_wrap</span>(<span class="sc">~</span>lambda)</span>
<span id="cb9-8"><a href="#cb9-8" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>p</span></code></pre></div>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="672" /></p>
<p>Jika kita tentukan <code>df=7</code>, maka hasil kurva model <code>smooth.spline</code> akan lebih merepresentasikan data</p>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb10"><pre class="sourceCode r"><code class="sourceCode r"><span id="cb10-1"><a href="#cb10-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>model_sms <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="fu">with</span>(<span class="at">data =</span> triceps,<span class="fu">smooth.spline</span>(age,triceps,<span class="at">df=</span><span class="dv">7</span>))</span>
<span id="cb10-2"><a href="#cb10-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>model_sms                  </span></code></pre></div>
<pre><code>## Call:
## smooth.spline(x = age, y = triceps, df = 7)
## 
## Smoothing Parameter  spar= 1.049874  lambda= 0.008827582 (11 iterations)
## Equivalent Degrees of Freedom (Df): 7.000747
## Penalized Criterion (RSS): 10112.16
## GCV: 14.20355</code></pre>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb12"><pre class="sourceCode r"><code class="sourceCode r"><span id="cb12-1"><a href="#cb12-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>pred_data <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> broom<span class="sc">::</span><span class="fu">augment</span>(model_sms)</span>
<span id="cb12-2"><a href="#cb12-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb12-3"><a href="#cb12-3" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">ggplot</span>(pred_data,<span class="fu">aes</span>(<span class="at">x=</span>x,<span class="at">y=</span>y))<span class="sc">+</span></span>
<span id="cb12-4"><a href="#cb12-4" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">geom_point</span>(<span class="at">alpha=</span><span class="fl">0.55</span>, <span class="at">color=</span><span class="st">&quot;black&quot;</span>)<span class="sc">+</span></span>
<span id="cb12-5"><a href="#cb12-5" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">geom_line</span>(<span class="fu">aes</span>(<span class="at">y=</span>.fitted),<span class="at">col=</span><span class="st">&quot;blue&quot;</span>,</span>
<span id="cb12-6"><a href="#cb12-6" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>            <span class="at">lty=</span><span class="dv">1</span>)<span class="sc">+</span></span>
<span id="cb12-7"><a href="#cb12-7" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">xlab</span>(<span class="st">&quot;age&quot;</span>)<span class="sc">+</span></span>
<span id="cb12-8"><a href="#cb12-8" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">ylab</span>(<span class="st">&quot;triceps&quot;</span>)<span class="sc">+</span></span>
<span id="cb12-9"><a href="#cb12-9" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">theme_bw</span>()</span></code></pre></div>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="672" /></p>
</div>
<div id="loess" class="section level2">
<h2>LOESS</h2>
<p>Masih menggunakan data <code>triceps</code> seperti pada ilustrasi sebelumnya, kali ini kita akan mencoba melakukan pendekatan <strong>local regression</strong> dengan fungsi <code>loess()</code>.</p>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb13"><pre class="sourceCode r"><code class="sourceCode r"><span id="cb13-1"><a href="#cb13-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>model_loess <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="fu">loess</span>(triceps<span class="sc">~</span>age,</span>
<span id="cb13-2"><a href="#cb13-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                     <span class="at">data =</span> triceps)</span>
<span id="cb13-3"><a href="#cb13-3" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">summary</span>(model_loess)</span></code></pre></div>
<pre><code>## Call:
## loess(formula = triceps ~ age, data = triceps)
## 
## Number of Observations: 892 
## Equivalent Number of Parameters: 4.6 
## Residual Standard Error: 3.777 
## Trace of smoother matrix: 5.01  (exact)
## 
## Control settings:
##   span     :  0.75 
##   degree   :  2 
##   family   :  gaussian
##   surface  :  interpolate      cell = 0.2
##   normalize:  TRUE
##  parametric:  FALSE
## drop.square:  FALSE</code></pre>
<p>Pengaruh parameter <code>span</code> terhadap tingkat smoothness kurva bisa dilihat dari ilustrasi berikut:</p>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb15"><pre class="sourceCode r"><code class="sourceCode r"><span id="cb15-1"><a href="#cb15-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>model_loess_span <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="fu">data.frame</span>(<span class="at">span=</span><span class="fu">seq</span>(<span class="fl">0.1</span>,<span class="dv">5</span>,<span class="at">by=</span><span class="fl">0.5</span>)) <span class="sc">%&gt;%</span> </span>
<span id="cb15-2"><a href="#cb15-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">group_by</span>(span) <span class="sc">%&gt;%</span> </span>
<span id="cb15-3"><a href="#cb15-3" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">do</span>(broom<span class="sc">::</span><span class="fu">augment</span>(<span class="fu">loess</span>(triceps<span class="sc">~</span>age,</span>
<span id="cb15-4"><a href="#cb15-4" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                     <span class="at">data =</span> triceps,<span class="at">span=</span>.<span class="sc">$</span>span)))</span></code></pre></div>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb16"><pre class="sourceCode r"><code class="sourceCode r"><span id="cb16-1"><a href="#cb16-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>p2 <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="fu">ggplot</span>(model_loess_span,</span>
<span id="cb16-2"><a href="#cb16-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>       <span class="fu">aes</span>(<span class="at">x=</span>age,<span class="at">y=</span>triceps))<span class="sc">+</span></span>
<span id="cb16-3"><a href="#cb16-3" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">geom_line</span>(<span class="fu">aes</span>(<span class="at">y=</span>.fitted),</span>
<span id="cb16-4"><a href="#cb16-4" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>            <span class="at">col=</span><span class="st">&quot;blue&quot;</span>,</span>
<span id="cb16-5"><a href="#cb16-5" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>            <span class="at">lty=</span><span class="dv">1</span></span>
<span id="cb16-6"><a href="#cb16-6" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>            )<span class="sc">+</span></span>
<span id="cb16-7"><a href="#cb16-7" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">facet_wrap</span>(<span class="sc">~</span>span)</span>
<span id="cb16-8"><a href="#cb16-8" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>p2</span></code></pre></div>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="672" /></p>
<p>Pendekatan ini juga dapat dilakukan dengan fungsi <code>stat_smooth()</code> pada package <code>ggplot2</code>.</p>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb17"><pre class="sourceCode r"><code class="sourceCode r"><span id="cb17-1"><a href="#cb17-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">library</span>(ggplot2)</span>
<span id="cb17-2"><a href="#cb17-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">ggplot</span>(triceps, <span class="fu">aes</span>(age,triceps)) <span class="sc">+</span></span>
<span id="cb17-3"><a href="#cb17-3" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">geom_point</span>(<span class="at">alpha=</span><span class="fl">0.5</span>,<span class="at">color=</span><span class="st">&quot;black&quot;</span>) <span class="sc">+</span></span>
<span id="cb17-4"><a href="#cb17-4" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">stat_smooth</span>(<span class="at">method=</span><span class="st">&#39;loess&#39;</span>,</span>
<span id="cb17-5"><a href="#cb17-5" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>               <span class="at">formula=</span>y<span class="sc">~</span>x,</span>
<span id="cb17-6"><a href="#cb17-6" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>              <span class="at">span =</span> <span class="fl">0.75</span>,</span>
<span id="cb17-7"><a href="#cb17-7" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>              <span class="at">col=</span><span class="st">&quot;blue&quot;</span>,</span>
<span id="cb17-8"><a href="#cb17-8" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>              <span class="at">lty=</span><span class="dv">1</span>,</span>
<span id="cb17-9"><a href="#cb17-9" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>              <span class="at">se=</span>F)</span></code></pre></div>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="672" /></p>
<p>Tuning <code>span</code> dapat dilakukan dengan menggunakan cross-validation</p>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb18"><pre class="sourceCode r"><code class="sourceCode r"><span id="cb18-1"><a href="#cb18-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">set.seed</span>(<span class="dv">123</span>)</span>
<span id="cb18-2"><a href="#cb18-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>cross_val <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="fu">vfold_cv</span>(triceps,<span class="at">v=</span><span class="dv">10</span>,<span class="at">strata =</span> <span class="st">&quot;triceps&quot;</span>)</span>
<span id="cb18-3"><a href="#cb18-3" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb18-4"><a href="#cb18-4" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>span <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="fu">seq</span>(<span class="fl">0.1</span>,<span class="dv">1</span>,<span class="at">length.out=</span><span class="dv">50</span>)</span>
<span id="cb18-5"><a href="#cb18-5" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb18-6"><a href="#cb18-6" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>best_loess <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="fu">map_dfr</span>(span, <span class="cf">function</span>(i){</span>
<span id="cb18-7"><a href="#cb18-7" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>metric_loess <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="fu">map_dfr</span>(cross_val<span class="sc">$</span>splits,</span>
<span id="cb18-8"><a href="#cb18-8" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>    <span class="cf">function</span>(x){</span>
<span id="cb18-9"><a href="#cb18-9" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>mod <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="fu">loess</span>(triceps <span class="sc">~</span> age,<span class="at">span =</span> i,</span>
<span id="cb18-10"><a href="#cb18-10" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>         <span class="at">data=</span>triceps[x<span class="sc">$</span>in_id,])</span>
<span id="cb18-11"><a href="#cb18-11" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>pred <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="fu">predict</span>(mod,</span>
<span id="cb18-12"><a href="#cb18-12" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>               <span class="at">newdata=</span>triceps[<span class="sc">-</span>x<span class="sc">$</span>in_id,])</span>
<span id="cb18-13"><a href="#cb18-13" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>truth <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> triceps[<span class="sc">-</span>x<span class="sc">$</span>in_id,]<span class="sc">$</span>triceps</span>
<span id="cb18-14"><a href="#cb18-14" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb18-15"><a href="#cb18-15" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>data_eval <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="fu">na.omit</span>(<span class="fu">data.frame</span>(<span class="at">pred=</span>pred,</span>
<span id="cb18-16"><a href="#cb18-16" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                                <span class="at">truth=</span>truth))</span>
<span id="cb18-17"><a href="#cb18-17" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb18-18"><a href="#cb18-18" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb18-19"><a href="#cb18-19" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>rmse <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> mlr3measures<span class="sc">::</span><span class="fu">rmse</span>(<span class="at">truth =</span> data_eval<span class="sc">$</span>truth,</span>
<span id="cb18-20"><a href="#cb18-20" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                           <span class="at">response =</span> data_eval<span class="sc">$</span>pred</span>
<span id="cb18-21"><a href="#cb18-21" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                           )</span>
<span id="cb18-22"><a href="#cb18-22" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>mae <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> mlr3measures<span class="sc">::</span><span class="fu">mae</span>(<span class="at">truth =</span> data_eval<span class="sc">$</span>truth,</span>
<span id="cb18-23"><a href="#cb18-23" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                           <span class="at">response =</span> data_eval<span class="sc">$</span>pred</span>
<span id="cb18-24"><a href="#cb18-24" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                           )</span>
<span id="cb18-25"><a href="#cb18-25" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>metric <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="fu">c</span>(rmse,mae)</span>
<span id="cb18-26"><a href="#cb18-26" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">names</span>(metric) <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="fu">c</span>(<span class="st">&quot;rmse&quot;</span>,<span class="st">&quot;mae&quot;</span>)</span>
<span id="cb18-27"><a href="#cb18-27" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">return</span>(metric)</span>
<span id="cb18-28"><a href="#cb18-28" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>}</span>
<span id="cb18-29"><a href="#cb18-29" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>)</span>
<span id="cb18-30"><a href="#cb18-30" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb18-31"><a href="#cb18-31" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">head</span>(metric_loess,<span class="dv">20</span>)</span>
<span id="cb18-32"><a href="#cb18-32" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb18-33"><a href="#cb18-33" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co"># menghitung rata-rata untuk 10 folds</span></span>
<span id="cb18-34"><a href="#cb18-34" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>mean_metric_loess <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="fu">colMeans</span>(metric_loess)</span>
<span id="cb18-35"><a href="#cb18-35" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb18-36"><a href="#cb18-36" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>mean_metric_loess</span>
<span id="cb18-37"><a href="#cb18-37" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>}</span>
<span id="cb18-38"><a href="#cb18-38" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>)</span>
<span id="cb18-39"><a href="#cb18-39" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb18-40"><a href="#cb18-40" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>best_loess <span class="ot">&lt;-</span> <span class="fu">cbind</span>(<span class="at">span=</span>span,best_loess)</span>
<span id="cb18-41"><a href="#cb18-41" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co"># menampilkan hasil all breaks</span></span>
<span id="cb18-42"><a href="#cb18-42" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>best_loess</span></code></pre></div>

<span id="cb21-2"><a href="#cb21-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">ggplot</span>(triceps, <span class="fu">aes</span>(age,triceps)) <span class="sc">+</span></span>

<span id="cb21-4"><a href="#cb21-4" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="fu">stat_smooth</span>(<span class="at">method=</span><span class="st">&#39;loess&#39;</span>,</span>
